```plantuml
@startuml andersonkmi_credit-card-bindb-service-aws

actor User

User -> "API Gateway": Request BIN Data Processing
"API Gateway" -> "S3": Retrieve CSV File
"S3" -> "Kinesis/SQS": Notify New CSV File

"Kinesis/SQS" -> "Lambda (CSV Processor)": Trigger on New File
"Lambda (CSV Processor)" -> "Lambda (Data Transformer)": Process CSV to Messages

"Lambda (Data Transformer)" -> "Kinesis/SQS": Send Processed Messages
"Kinesis/SQS" -> "Lambda (Data Storer)": Trigger on Message

"Lambda (Data Storer)" -> "DynamoDB": Store Processed BIN Data

@enduml
```